# Copy to ".env" in the project root (see README). Never commit real values.
#
# Use Supabase **Transaction pooler** on port **6543** (same db.*.supabase.co host) when
# direct port 5432 fails on IPv4. If 6543 still fails, copy the exact URI from:
# Supabase → Project Settings → Database → Connection string → Transaction pooler.

# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:URL_ENCODED_PASSWORD@db.YOUR_REF.supabase.co:6543/postgres?sslmode=require
# SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_REF.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_KEY=your_key_here
